summary:
Enjoys working with young people. Very systematic in approach, values-driven, organized, and determined.

Objective: To inspire, by teaching children and young people so that they can make the most of life. I want to make a big impact on students' learning, and seek for opportunities to develop myself professionally as a teacher in order to be more effective.
